    "body": "The bitcoin-dev mailing list moved from lists.linuxfoundation.org to Google Groups. The old archive URLs no longer resolve.\n\nThis updates the two remaining dead links (not covered by #1698) to their gnusha.org archive equivalents:\n\n- **BIP-077** (`bip-0077.md`): `bitcoin-dev/2021-January/018358.html` → [gnusha.org archive](https://gnusha.org/pi/bitcoindev/CAPR5oBPJPs1g32K3XDnNyV3bKCq58fti3mNd-ooFhKNMVxCf9g@mail.gmail.com/) (PayJoin adoption discussion)\n- **BIP-348** (`bip-0348.md`): `bitcoin-dev/2021-July/019192.html` → [gnusha.org archive](https://gnusha.org/pi/bitcoindev/CAD5xwhjmu-Eee47Ho5eA6E6+aAdnchLU0OVZo=RTHaXnN17x8A@mail.gmail.com/) (CHECKSIGFROMSTACK mailing list thread)\n\nUnlike #1698 which uses the `gnusha.org/url/` redirect service, these links resolve directly to the archived messages via their Message-ID.",
